description:
PANTS with Kate Moennig and Leisha Hailey

Produced by Melisa D. Monts and Diamond MPrint Productions

Edited by Diane Kang 

 

Leisha feeds her house guest a yam. Kate rushes to a haircut. Then they ponder why cheating is so prominent in not just “The L World” but every soap opera.
